WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:04.230
Good morning, family. I have a heavy

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:08.030
word to give today. I made the

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:10.270
recording whenever I was in the

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:13.549
spirit and what the Lord showed me, but

00:00:13.559 --> 00:00:16.070
after watching it back, I really want

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:18.750
to get across

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:21.429
how heavy this word really was. You know

00:00:21.439 --> 00:00:25.029
when you watch old World War II movies

00:00:25.039 --> 00:00:27.630
and how heavy those movies were? The

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.710
Jewish people being taken into

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:35.190
concentration camps, that heavy

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.830
vibe,

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:41.310
people suffering, people going through

00:00:41.310 --> 00:00:41.320
trials

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:46.630
from the Nazis, and

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.590
all that was going on in World War

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:51.350
II. It was a very hard

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:55.189
time in world

00:00:55.199 --> 00:00:57.590
history. Whenever I'm praying and

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.670
seeing over, and the Lord's showing me in

00:00:59.670 --> 00:00:59.680
a

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:02.709
vision, the heaviness of

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:07.310
what He showed me is... I'm trying to

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.070
let you be able to relate to it. It's

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:12.830
that heaviness

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:16.710
when you see pictures of people

00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:18.990
during the Great Depression and how they

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:22.149
look very somber and how they don't have

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:24.109
a lot of joy on their face.

00:01:24.119 --> 00:01:25.910
It's just a

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:28.390
heavy time—the Great Depression, the

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:31.190
way everybody was.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:34.190
It was just intense. So

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.630
whenever you're seeing over in the

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:37.469
spirit, you're seeing this stuff and

00:01:37.479 --> 00:01:40.190
the outpouring, and

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:43.630
you're trying to

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.870
decipher

00:01:45.870 --> 00:01:45.880
and

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:48.230
put it into words in the natural what

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.030
you're seeing in the spirit. You

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.149
don't want to add anything to it and you

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.350
don't want to take anything away. I want

00:01:54.360 --> 00:01:57.670
to convey what I saw so that

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:59.950
you're able to get the message that I

00:01:59.950 --> 00:01:59.960
saw

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:02.510
in the spirit.

00:02:02.520 --> 00:02:04.350
Like I said, you don't want to add

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:06.310
your opinion to it. He said, 'Brandon, there

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:09.510
is a great shaking coming. You have to

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:12.470
warn My people. What is about to take

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:16.390
place is not Me departing. It is

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.190
not a departing.'He said, 'Many will call

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:22.509
this, Brandon, an

00:02:22.509 --> 00:02:22.519
Ichabod.'He

00:02:22.519 --> 00:02:24.750
told me,

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:27.589
'They will call this the Great

00:02:27.589 --> 00:02:27.599
Ichabod,

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:31.150
but it is not an Ichabod.'He said, 'I am

00:02:31.160 --> 00:02:33.869
going to shake the

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:37.390
church, I'm going to shake America, I'm

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:39.910
going to shake the world.'He said there

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:43.630
is a massive

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:45.790
Refiner's Fire that is going to take

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:48.910
place upon the world because My

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:51.790
bride and My people are asleep. And He

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:55.550
said in this Refiner's Fire,

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:58.309
'You will go through a desert season.

00:02:58.319 --> 00:03:00.350
It will feel like a desert season.

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:02.949
It will feel that I have abandoned

00:03:02.959 --> 00:03:05.949
you for what's coming, America. It will

00:03:05.959 --> 00:03:09.070
feel that I have deserted

00:03:09.070 --> 00:03:09.080
you.'And

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:11.470
then He kept using the word

00:03:11.470 --> 00:03:11.480
Ichabod.

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:13.550
It's going to feel like an Ichabod.

00:03:13.550 --> 00:03:13.560
I had

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:15.630
no idea what that word means,

00:03:15.640 --> 00:03:18.070
but He said it will feel that

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.830
there's a great Ichabod upon the land. He

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:23.190
said, 'But I have not abandoned you.

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:23.200
I

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:26.190
have not forsaken you.

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:28.710
I'm just in this time of a test.'He said

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:31.309
there's going to be a time of testing,

00:03:31.319 --> 00:03:34.030
and He said in this test, 'You do

00:03:34.040 --> 00:03:36.309
not speak to the students when they're

00:03:36.319 --> 00:03:38.869
going through the test.'But there is

00:03:38.869 --> 00:03:38.879
a remnant

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:42.229
of people that

00:03:42.239 --> 00:03:46.190
woke up with the last round of the

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:48.830
wave that came—the first wave of COVID. He

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:51.229
said there was a great wave that came

00:03:51.239 --> 00:03:53.869
and a lot of people woke up during

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:56.030
that, but it was a small percentage.

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:58.789
He

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:00.550
said, 'Son, if you've already passed the

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.390
test and you're already awake through

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.949
the Refiner's Fire, you don't go

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:07.229
through it again because you're

00:04:07.229 --> 00:04:07.239
awake.'But

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:10.309
just like the children of

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:12.830
Israel, whenever they put the

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:15.949
blood on the door and the death

00:04:15.959 --> 00:04:18.150
angel passed through, He said they

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:20.509
could hear the wails and the cries of the

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:22.550
people that were going

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:25.270
through the judgment of what was

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:28.150
happening on Egypt. But this

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:31.430
will not be a judgment; this is a

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:31.440
shaking.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.510
It is an awakening that's about to

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:36.870
happen. He said, 'Yes, you

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:39.430
will be in amongst the people and you

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:42.510
will see all the stuff going on, but it

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:44.670
does not have to affect you in your

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:47.270
house if you're awake.'He said, 'Don't let

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:49.590
the fear of what's going on get inside

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:52.390
of you, for I'm awakening the

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:55.830
church, I'm awakening

00:04:55.830 --> 00:04:55.840
the people.'Many

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:57.350
people

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.710
are going to get mad and say, 'God's

00:04:59.710 --> 00:04:59.720
judgment,

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:02.150
all it's Ichabod.'Like this word

00:05:02.150 --> 00:05:02.160
Ichabod,

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.550
you're going to feel this way,

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:06.189
that He's departed

00:05:06.199 --> 00:05:08.070
from America

00:05:08.070 --> 00:05:08.080
and

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.550
from the earth. It's going

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:12.430
to be a great shaking. But in this, He said,

00:05:12.440 --> 00:05:13.990
'The people that are

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:16.830
awake, you will be the salt and

00:05:16.830 --> 00:05:16.840
the light.'He

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:18.710
said they will come to you and you'll

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:21.550
have a sense of instruction to

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.350
encourage them and tell them it's going

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:26.670
to be okay. On the other side of this

00:05:26.670 --> 00:05:26.680
Ichabod,

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.350
what you feel is an

00:05:29.350 --> 00:05:29.360
Ichabod,

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:32.670
I saw a great, glorious

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:35.950
church. After that shaking

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:38.430
happens, they will rise up out of

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:43.990
this Potter's

00:05:43.990 --> 00:05:44.000
wheel,

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.029
this pressure from the Potter's

00:05:46.029 --> 00:05:46.039
wheel.

00:05:46.039 --> 00:05:47.909
They will rise up out of that. When

00:05:47.919 --> 00:05:50.670
they go through the fire, it will be

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:54.309
like a glazed church. It will

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:57.670
be the shiny pot that

00:05:57.680 --> 00:06:00.629
He desires it to be.

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:02.430
There is a great

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:04.990
revival coming, but it will come through

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:08.629
great pressure and great

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:11.150
pain to

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:15.350
the flesh, to your

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:17.629
mind, will, and emotions. It makes

00:06:17.639 --> 00:06:21.189
you grow. He brought up to

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:24.550
me that it will be like

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:27.629
a caterpillar in a cocoon.

00:06:34.199 --> 00:06:36.309
If you take

00:06:36.319 --> 00:06:38.469
and you would slice

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:40.990
open

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:42.990
that

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:45.629
cocoon and help

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:48.350
that butterfly out, it never develops. It

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:50.270
never gets to strengthen its

00:06:50.280 --> 00:06:52.790
wings to fly. It will stay there

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:54.790
dormant and not

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:57.070
become anything. But if you let that

00:06:57.080 --> 00:06:58.909
pressure of that cocoon on that

00:06:58.919 --> 00:07:01.869
butterfly keep pushing,

00:07:05.639 --> 00:07:07.950
when he gets

00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:10.550
out of that cocoon, he becomes a

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:13.350
beautiful thing and it flies. It was

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:16.309
through the pressure through that cocoon

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:18.909
that made that butterfly who it was. But

00:07:18.919 --> 00:07:21.710
if you remove that cocoon, that

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:23.550
butterfly is dwarfed and it never

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.869
becomes what it's supposed to be.

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:27.990
And that's what it's going to be for you.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:29.510
You're going to go through some

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:30.950
pressure, through some

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:32.950
hard times where you think you

00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:34.390
can't even get through it. You're going

00:07:34.400 --> 00:07:36.790
to think God abandoned

00:07:36.790 --> 00:07:36.800
you,

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:38.710
but God has not

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:40.909
abandoned you.

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:48.149
Through that cocoon, you will become

00:07:48.159 --> 00:07:50.430
the beautiful butterfly that God has

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:52.869
called you to be. It may look like

00:07:52.879 --> 00:07:54.830
it's not going to get over; it may look

00:07:54.840 --> 00:07:57.070
like things are falling apart, but you

00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:58.909
keep pushing, you keep stretching, you

00:07:58.919 --> 00:08:01.430
keep moving your wings. In that

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:03.270
pressure, that pressure is what's going

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:06.189
to create that beautiful pot, that

00:08:06.199 --> 00:08:07.990
beautiful butterfly coming out of that

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.189
cocoon.

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:16.430
Many people are living in sin,

00:08:16.440 --> 00:08:18.029
many people are living in

00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:20.309
compromise, and you say, 'Oh, the grace

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:22.270
message,'or,

00:08:22.280 --> 00:08:24.350
'God would never let this happen to me, we're

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:26.710
going in the Rapture.'But God said

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:29.110
He's coming back for a pure bride

00:08:29.110 --> 00:08:29.120
without

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:31.749
spot or wrinkle.

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:34.230
I'm telling you, there is going to be a

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.750
great shaking take place. Not only for America—I've seen this, and

00:08:36.750 --> 00:08:36.760
yes it will be

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:39.550
for

00:08:39.560 --> 00:08:41.589
the

00:08:44.110 --> 00:08:44.120
world—but

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:48.389
He speaks to me prophetically for

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:51.710
America. He told me it

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:55.430
will feel, in this place where we've

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:57.670
always been spoiled,

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:05.150
'I've abandoned you for what's about to

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:07.269
happen. It will feel that you are in an

00:09:07.269 --> 00:09:07.279
Ichabod.'But

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:10.750
He said, 'I have not left

00:09:10.750 --> 00:09:10.760
you.'And

00:09:10.760 --> 00:09:12.670
I keep rehearsing that: 'I have not

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:14.990
left you, son.'He said when you're

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:18.710
going through a major test, the

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:21.069
teacher and the principal

00:09:21.069 --> 00:09:21.079
are

00:09:21.079 --> 00:09:23.389
silent.

00:09:23.399 --> 00:09:27.190
They're silent

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:29.910
in the test until you pass the test,

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.990
and then I'll tell

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.110
you your grade.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:38.509
It will be like that for what's

00:09:38.519 --> 00:09:41.710
coming. I know this might be

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:44.350
a heavy word, but you need to hear it.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:46.550
There is a second wave about to take

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:48.590
place.

00:09:58.560 --> 00:10:00.949
I believe whatever this is, it's

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:04.350
financial.

00:10:07.959 --> 00:10:09.750
He showed me

00:10:09.750 --> 00:10:09.760
that

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:11.790
those that are listening to Me, those

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:14.269
that are awake, are going to

00:10:14.279 --> 00:10:16.670
hear Me and take heed to what I'm

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:19.230
saying to prepare.

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.630
But if you are

00:10:25.640 --> 00:10:27.630
watching this video and you're awake, you

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:29.590
better be praying in the spirit,

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:31.509
seeking Him with prayer and

00:10:31.519 --> 00:10:34.150
fasting, listening to His voice, because

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.629
there are very hard

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:39.990
days, very sobering days coming to a lot

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:42.150
of people. They're going to feel

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:44.150
like there's an Ichabod on their

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:46.230
life. But

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:51.670
there will be a

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:54.069
people that press into Him.

00:10:54.079 --> 00:10:55.750
I can tell

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:57.910
you from

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.110
experience, there would be times whenever

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:02.389
I was going through my

00:11:02.389 --> 00:11:02.399
Refiner's

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:06.990
Fire that I thought God had

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:10.389
left. There were such hard times. I

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:12.629
remember driving

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:15.030
home from work and saying, 'God, why

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:17.870
are you silent? Where have you

00:11:20.839 --> 00:11:23.829
gone?'But

00:11:26.079 --> 00:11:27.870
He would always encourage me and

00:11:27.880 --> 00:11:30.110
give me that tug inside of my spirit to

00:11:30.120 --> 00:11:32.550
say, 'I'm still there,

00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:32.560
Brandon.'On

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:34.470
the

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.389
other side of the pressure and

00:11:36.399 --> 00:11:38.910
the pain, it's going to be beautiful for

00:11:38.920 --> 00:11:41.910
you. But if I remove that cocoon off of

00:11:41.920 --> 00:11:43.949
your life, buddy, you're never

00:11:43.959 --> 00:11:45.750
going to develop into who I've called you

00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:48.949
to be. So in the pressure

00:11:48.949 --> 00:11:48.959
of

00:11:48.959 --> 00:11:51.350
the Potter's

00:11:51.350 --> 00:11:51.360
wheel,

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:54.350
you've got to just say,

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:58.389
'God, not my will but Yours be

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:00.150
done.'Do

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:02.230
everything you can in your life without

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:04.470
grumbling and

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:07.430
complaining. Father, I choose to worship

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:10.949
You today.

00:12:16.279 --> 00:12:18.550
When Joseph was doing

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:21.470
everything he could to follow the

00:12:21.480 --> 00:12:24.550
Lord, he fled from the woman trying

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:27.949
to have a relationship with him

00:12:27.959 --> 00:12:31.310
in adultery. He fled and took his coat

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:34.870
off. But because of her

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:34.880
falsely

00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:36.990
accusing

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:39.829
him,

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:47.310
he was thrown in prison. In that, he

00:12:47.320 --> 00:12:49.790
refused to curse God. He still worshiped

00:12:49.800 --> 00:12:52.430
Him in that pressure of that Refiner's

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:56.670
Fire, and that pressure lasted for years.

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:04.470
He knew the promise.

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:14.430
There was

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:17.710
a process for Joseph all throughout

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:20.590
his story:

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:23.590
sold into slavery,

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:26.230
thrown

00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:28.949
into prison, then he interpreted the dream.

00:13:36.959 --> 00:13:38.670
He didn't know

00:13:38.670 --> 00:13:38.680
that

00:13:38.680 --> 00:13:40.269
in

00:13:40.269 --> 00:13:40.279
ten

00:13:40.279 --> 00:13:43.110
hours

